    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-12-01T15:51:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-12-01T15:51:00-05:00" n="857"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d857">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Day</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_imprecise-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1898-12-01T21:00:00+00:09">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 1, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 35.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>At this time, Thursday, 8.30 p.m., we have received no answer to our telegram
                    asking for instruction as to Spanish rights in ports of Cuba and Puerto Rico and
                    concerning Kusaie. It is important to have same to-morrow.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-12-01T21:00:00+00:09">Thursday
                            evening, 9</date>.</dateline>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Day.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
